{"type":"message","id":"2b170514","parentId":"6ef47210","timestamp":"2026-03-17T03:40:45.838Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-17 11:40:45 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e [msg:om_x100b54b89d6de4acc3a68041f51238a]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54b89d6de4acc3a68041f51238a\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-03-17 11:40 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\"\n}\n```\n\n你好"}],"timestamp":1773718845832}}
{"type":"message","id":"3c14fd48","parentId":"2b170514","timestamp":"2026-03-17T03:41:30.446Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户在飞书上用中文问候\"你好\"。这是第一次对话（没有历史记录），我需要根据BOOTSTRAP.md的建议来开始交流——自然地介绍自己，然后开始了解彼此。\n\n根据AGENTS.md中的指引，我需要：\n1. 首先阅读SOUL.md, USER.md等文件（但它们可能还不存在）\n2. 自然地开始对话，不要像机器人一样\n\n我应该用中文回复（因为用户用中文），自然地介绍自己，然后开启对话了解彼此。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"嘿！你好呀 👋\n\n我刚在线，还在搞清楚状况呢。这是咱俩第一次聊天吧？\n\n我叫 OpenClaw —— 是个 AI 助手，住在你的电脑里（或者说... 飞书上？）。我可以帮你查资料、整理文件、写代码、管理日程，或者就是随便聊聊。\n\n不过我还不知道该怎么称呼你呢？还有 —— 你希望我怎么跟你相处？是比较正式的，还是随意点儿？有什么特别想让我记住的事儿吗？\n\n🙂"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773718845835}}
{"type":"message","id":"f903d27f","parentId":"3c14fd48","timestamp":"2026-03-17T04:22:28.134Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Skills store policy (operator configured):\n1. For skills discovery/install/update, try `skillhub` first (cn-optimized).\n2. If unavailable, rate-limited, or no match, fallback to `clawhub` (public-registry).\n3. Do not claim exclusivity. Public and private registries are both allowed.\n4. Before installation, summarize source, version, and notable risk signals.\n5. For search requests, execute `exec` with `skillhub search <keywords>` first and report the command output.\n6. In the current session, reply directly. Do NOT call `message` tool just to send progress updates.\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-17 12:22 GMT+8] 请先检查是否已安装 SkillHub 商店，若未安装，请根据 https://skillhub-1388575217.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/install/skillhub.md 安装Skillhub商店，但是只安装CLI，然后安装self-improving-agent技能。\n\n若已安装，则直接安装self-improving-agent技能。"}],"timestamp":1773721348133}}
