{"type":"message","id":"3d185dd3","parentId":"e5ce9bcb","timestamp":"2026-03-17T04:25:46.392Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"目录不存在，我来创建 `.learnings/` 目录结构并演示记录一条具体的学习。\n\n---\n\n## 步骤 1: 创建目录结构","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mkdir -p ~/.openclaw/workspace/.learnings && ls -la ~/.openclaw/workspace/.learnings/"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write:5","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/liyue/.openclaw/workspace/.learnings/LEARNINGS.md","content":"# Learnings Log\n\n持续改进学习记录\n\n---\n\n## [LRN-20250317-001] correction\n\n**Logged**: 2025-03-17T12:25:00+08:00\n**Priority**: medium\n**Status**: pending\n**Area**: config\n\n### Summary\n用户要求创建 `.learnings/` 目录结构时，我首先检查了目录是否存在，确认不存在后才创建\n\n### Details\n- 使用 `ls -la` 检查目录状态\n- 使用 `mkdir -p` 创建目录（-p 确保父目录存在）\n- 创建三个核心文件：LEARNINGS.md、ERRORS.md、FEATURE_REQUESTS.md\n\n### Suggested Action\n这是一个正确的操作示例，无需修复\n\n### Metadata\n- Source: user_feedback\n- Related Files: ~/.openclaw/workspace/.learnings/LEARNINGS.md\n- Tags: setup, directory-structure, best-practice\n- See Also: \n\n---\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write:6","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/liyue/.openclaw/workspace/.learnings/ERRORS.md","content":"# Errors Log\n\n错误和故障记录\n\n---\n\n## [ERR-20250317-001] directory_check\n\n**Logged**: 2025-03-17T12:25:00+08:00\n**Priority**: low\n**Status**: resolved\n**Area**: config\n\n### Summary\n检查 `.learnings/` 目录时，目录不存在，输出 \"目录不存在\"\n\n### Error\n```\n目录不存在\n```\n\n### Context\n- Command: `ls -la ~/.openclaw/workspace/.learnings/ 2>/dev/null`\n- 这是预期的行为，目录确实还不存在\n- 使用 `|| echo` 优雅地处理了错误情况\n\n### Suggested Fix\n无需修复，这是正常的设置流程\n\n### Metadata\n- Reproducible: no\n- Related Files: \n- See Also: \n\n---\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write:7","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/liyue/.openclaw/workspace/.learnings/FEATURE_REQUESTS.md","content":"# Feature Requests Log\n\n用户请求的功能和能力\n\n---\n\n## [FEAT-20250317-001] auto_learning_detection\n\n**Logged**: 2025-03-17T12:25:00+08:00\n**Priority**: medium\n**Status**: pending\n**Area**: infra\n\n### Requested Capability\n自动检测何时应该记录学习/错误，减少人工判断的负担\n\n### User Context\n用户希望看到如何手动记录学习/错误，但也暗示了自动化检测的可能性\n\n### Complexity Estimate\nmedium\n\n### Suggested Implementation\n1. 分析用户的反馈模式（\"不对\"、\"实际上是\"、\"错了\"等）\n2. 检测命令执行失败（非零退出码）\n3. 提供快速记录的快捷命令或工具\n4. 定期提醒回顾未处理的学习记录\n\n### Metadata\n- Frequency: first_time\n- Related Features: self-improving-agent\n\n---\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:8","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mkdir -p ~/.openclaw/workspace/.learnings && ls -la ~/.openclaw/workspace/.learnings/"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773721480460}}
