{"type":"message","id":"27f4d221","parentId":"f523a264","timestamp":"2026-03-17T04:26:16.713Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，目录和文件都创建成功了。现在让我来展示一下这些文件的内容，并解释每条记录的结构。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"已完成演示！目录和文件都已创建。让我展示一下记录的结构：\n\n---\n\n## 📁 创建的目录结构\n\n```\n~/.openclaw/workspace/.learnings/\n├── LEARNINGS.md      # 学习记录（用户纠正、最佳实践等）\n├── ERRORS.md         # 错误记录（命令失败、API故障等）\n└── FEATURE_REQUESTS.md # 功能请求\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📝 示例记录解析\n\n### 1. 学习记录 (LEARNINGS.md)\n\n```\n## [LRN-20250317-001] correction   ← 唯一ID + 类别\n\n**Logged**: 2025-03-17T12:25:00+08:00\n**Priority**: medium                    ← low/medium/high/critical\n**Status**: pending                     ← pending/in_progress/resolved\n**Area**: config                        ← frontend/backend/infra/tests/docs/config\n\n### Summary\n一句话概括学习的内容\n\n### Details\n详细背景：发生了什么、原来的理解是什么、正确的是什么\n\n### Suggested Action\n建议的修复或改进措施\n\n### Metadata\n- Source: conversation|error|user_feedback\n- Related Files: 相关文件路径\n- Tags: 标签1, 标签2\n- See Also: LRN-20250316-001 (关联的其他记录)\n```\n\n### 2. 错误记录 (ERRORS.md)\n\n关键区别在于包含 `Error` 区块显示实际错误输出，以及 `Reproducible` 字段标记是否可重现。\n\n### 3. 功能请求 (FEATURE_REQUESTS.md)\n\n包含 `Requested Capability`（请求的功能）、`Complexity Estimate`（复杂度评估：simple/medium/complex）和 `Suggested Implementation`（建议实现方案）。\n\n---\n\n## 💡 使用流程\n\n```\n触发条件 → 选择文件 → 填写记录 → 定期回顾 → 推广有价值的内容\n    ↓\n  用户纠正 → LEARNINGS.md\n  命令失败 → ERRORS.md\n  功能请求 → FEATURE_REQUESTS.md\n```\n\n需要我演示**如何查看已有记录**或**如何将学习推广到 SOUL.md/AGENTS.md** 吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773721546486}}
