{"type":"message","id":"ec5acd28","parentId":"d933afdc","timestamp":"2026-03-17T04:37:08.377Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Skills store policy (operator configured):\n1. For skills discovery/install/update, try `skillhub` first (cn-optimized).\n2. If unavailable, rate-limited, or no match, fallback to `clawhub` (public-registry).\n3. Do not claim exclusivity. Public and private registries are both allowed.\n4. Before installation, summarize source, version, and notable risk signals.\n5. For search requests, execute `exec` with `skillhub search <keywords>` first and report the command output.\n6. In the current session, reply directly. Do NOT call `message` tool just to send progress updates.\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-17 12:37 GMT+8] 安装怎么样了"}],"timestamp":1773722228376}}
{"type":"message","id":"15a107b0","parentId":"ec5acd28","timestamp":"2026-03-17T04:37:15.348Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户询问安装进度，根据上下文，我之前已经安装了 frontend-design 技能，现在应该告诉用户结果。让我检查一下安装状态。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"安装已完成！✅\n\n**安装状态：**\n\n| 技能 | 状态 | 路径 |\n|------|------|------|\n| self-improving-agent | ✅ 已安装 | `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/self-improving-agent` |\n| frontend-design | ✅ 已安装 | `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/frontend-design` |\n\n两个技能都已成功安装，可以直接使用了。需要我帮你查看 frontend-design 技能的具体功能吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773722228377}}
{"type":"message","id":"41c87267","parentId":"15a107b0","timestamp":"2026-03-17T04:37:28.096Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Skills store policy (operator configured):\n1. For skills discovery/install/update, try `skillhub` first (cn-optimized).\n2. If unavailable, rate-limited, or no match, fallback to `clawhub` (public-registry).\n3. Do not claim exclusivity. Public and private registries are both allowed.\n4. Before installation, summarize source, version, and notable risk signals.\n5. For search requests, execute `exec` with `skillhub search <keywords>` first and report the command output.\n6. In the current session, reply directly. Do NOT call `message` tool just to send progress updates.\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-17 12:37 GMT+8] 查看 frontend-design 技能的具体功能"}],"timestamp":1773722248094}}
{"type":"message","id":"b9c8f6a8","parentId":"41c87267","timestamp":"2026-03-17T04:37:31.025Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想查看 frontend-design 技能的具体功能。我需要读取该技能的 SKILL.md 文件。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"read:10","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/liyue/.openclaw/workspace/skills/frontend-design/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773722248095}}
{"type":"message","id":"5cb2509c","parentId":"b9c8f6a8","timestamp":"2026-03-17T04:37:31.054Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"read:10","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: frontend-design\ndescription: Create distinctive, production-grade frontend interfaces with high design quality. Use this skill when the user asks to build web components, pages, or applications. Generates creative, polished code that avoids generic AI aesthetics.\nlicense: Complete terms in LICENSE.txt\n---\n\nThis skill guides creation of distinctive, production-grade frontend interfaces that avoid generic \"AI slop\" aesthetics. Implement real working code with exceptional attention to aesthetic details and creative choices.\n\nThe user provides frontend requirements: a component, page, application, or interface to build. They may include context about the purpose, audience, or technical constraints.\n\n## Design Thinking\n\nBefore coding, understand the context and commit to a BOLD aesthetic direction:\n- **Purpose**: What problem does this interface solve? Who uses it?\n- **Tone**: Pick an extreme: brutally minimal, maximalist chaos, retro-futuristic, organic/natural, luxury/refined, playful/toy-like, editorial/magazine, brutalist/raw, art deco/geometric, soft/pastel, industrial/utilitarian, etc. There are so many flavors to choose from. Use these for inspiration but design one that is true to the aesthetic direction.\n- **Constraints**: Technical requirements (framework, performance, accessibility).\n- **Differentiation**: What makes this UNFORGETTABLE? What's the one thing someone will remember?\n\n**CRITICAL**: Choose a clear conceptual direction and execute it with precision. Bold maximalism and refined minimalism both work - the key is intentionality, not intensity.\n\nThen implement working code (HTML/CSS/JS, React, Vue, etc.) that is:\n- Production-grade and functional\n- Visually striking and memorable\n- Cohesive with a clear aesthetic point-of-view\n- Meticulously refined in every detail\n\n## Frontend Aesthetics Guidelines\n\nFocus on:\n- **Typography**: Choose fonts that are beautiful, unique, and interesting. Avoid generic fonts like Arial and Inter; opt instead for distinctive choices that elevate the frontend's aesthetics; unexpected, characterful font choices. Pair a distinctive display font with a refined body font.\n- **Color & Theme**: Commit to a cohesive aesthetic. Use CSS variables for consistency. Dominant colors with sharp accents outperform timid, evenly-distributed palettes.\n- **Motion**: Use animations for effects and micro-interactions. Prioritize CSS-only solutions for HTML. Use Motion library for React when available. Focus on high-impact moments: one well-orchestrated page load with staggered reveals (animation-delay) creates more delight than scattered micro-interactions. Use scroll-triggering and hover states that surprise.\n- **Spatial Composition**: Unexpected layouts. Asymmetry. Overlap. Diagonal flow. Grid-breaking elements. Generous negative space OR controlled density.\n- **Backgrounds & Visual Details**: Create atmosphere and depth rather than defaulting to solid colors. Add contextual effects and textures that match the overall aesthetic. Apply creative forms like gradient meshes, noise textures, geometric patterns, layered transparencies, dramatic shadows, decorative borders, custom cursors, and grain overlays.\n\nNEVER use generic AI-generated aesthetics like overused font families (Inter, Roboto, Arial, system fonts), cliched color schemes (particularly purple gradients on white backgrounds), predictable layouts and component patterns, and cookie-cutter design that lacks context-specific character.\n\nInterpret creatively and make unexpected choices that feel genuinely designed for the context. No design should be the same. Vary between light and dark themes, different fonts, different aesthetics. NEVER converge on common choices (Space Grotesk, for example) across generations.\n\n**IMPORTANT**: Match implementation complexity to the aesthetic vision. Maximalist designs need elaborate code with extensive animations and effects. Minimalist or refined designs need restraint, precision, and careful attention to spacing, typography, and subtle details. Elegance comes from executing the vision well.\n\nRemember: Claude is capable of extraordinary creative work. Don't hold back, show what can truly be created when thinking outside the box and committing fully to a distinctive vision.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773722251048}}
{"type":"message","id":"14b41079","parentId":"5cb2509c","timestamp":"2026-03-17T04:39:07.456Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"## frontend-design 技能详解\n\n这是一个**前端界面设计技能**，专注于创建**独特、高品质、生产级**的前端界面，避免那种千篇一律的\"AI 生成感\"。\n\n---\n\n### 🎯 核心用途\n\n| 场景 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| 构建 Web 组件 | 按钮、卡片、表单、导航等 |\n| 开发页面 | 落地页、仪表盘、详情页等 |\n| 完整应用 | 单页应用、管理后台等 |\n\n---\n\n### ✨ 设计理念（区别于普通 AI 生成）\n\n这个技能强调**独特美学**和**创意执行**：\n\n#### 1. **大胆的美学方向**\n- 极简主义 或 极繁主义\n- 复古未来主义\n- 有机/自然风格\n- 奢华/精致感\n- 俏皮/玩具风格\n- 编辑/杂志风\n- 粗野主义\n- 装饰艺术/几何风格\n\n#### 2. **避免\"AI 俗套\"**\n❌ 不要：\n- Inter、Roboto、Arial 等通用字体\n- 紫色渐变配白底\n- 可预测的组件模式\n- 缺乏上下文特色的设计\n\n✅ 要：\n- 独特、有个性的字体选择\n- 有主见的配色方案\n- 不对称布局\n- 意外的视觉元素\n\n#### 3. **技术实现要点**\n\n| 方面 | 要求 |\n|------|------|\n| **字体** | 选择美观、独特、有趣的字体，避免通用字体 |\n| **颜色** | 使用 CSS 变量保持一致性，主导色+强调色 |\n| **动效** | CSS 动画用于效果，React 可用 Motion 库，聚焦关键时刻 |\n| **空间构图** | 意外布局、不对称、重叠、对角线流动、打破网格 |\n| **背景细节** | 渐变网格、噪点纹理、几何图案、分层透明、戏剧性阴影 |\n\n---\n\n### 🛠️ 使用方式\n\n当你需要构建前端界面时，直接描述你的需求：\n\n```\n\"帮我做一个复古未来风格的登录页面\"\n\"需要一个极简主义的数据仪表盘\"\n\"做一个有机自然风格的个人博客首页\"\n```\n\n技能会引导生成**独特、可投入生产**的代码，而不是千篇一律的模板。\n\n---\n\n### 📋 总结\n\n| 特性 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| **目标** | 独特、高品质、生产级前端界面 |\n| **区别** | 避免通用\"AI 美学\"，强调创意和个性 |\n| **覆盖** | 组件、页面、完整应用 |\n| **技术** | HTML/CSS/JS、React、Vue 等 |\n| **重点** | 字体、颜色、动效、空间构图、背景细节 |\n\n需要我用这个技能帮你创建某个具体的界面吗？比如一个独特风格的落地页或组件？","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## frontend-design 技能详解\n\n这是一个**前端界面设计技能**，专注于创建**独特、高品质、生产级**的前端界面，避免那种千篇一律的\"AI 生成感\"。\n\n---\n\n### 🎯 核心用途\n\n| 场景 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| 构建 Web 组件 | 按钮、卡片、表单、导航等 |\n| 开发页面 | 落地页、仪表盘、详情页等 |\n| 完整应用 | 单页应用、管理后台等 |\n\n---\n\n### ✨ 设计理念（区别于普通 AI 生成）\n\n这个技能强调**独特美学**和**创意执行**：\n\n#### 1. **大胆的美学方向**\n- 极简主义 或 极繁主义\n- 复古未来主义\n- 有机/自然风格\n- 奢华/精致感\n- 俏皮/玩具风格\n- 编辑/杂志风\n- 粗野主义\n- 装饰艺术/几何风格\n\n#### 2. **避免\"AI 俗套\"**\n❌ 不要：\n- Inter、Roboto、Arial 等通用字体\n- 紫色渐变配白底\n- 可预测的组件模式\n- 缺乏上下文特色的设计\n\n✅ 要：\n- 独特、有个性的字体选择\n- 有主见的配色方案\n- 不对称布局\n- 意外的视觉元素\n\n#### 3. **技术实现要点**\n\n| 方面 | 要求 |\n|------|------|\n| **字体** | 选择美观、独特、有趣的字体，避免通用字体 |\n| **颜色** | 使用 CSS 变量保持一致性，主导色+强调色 |\n| **动效** | CSS 动画用于效果，React 可用 Motion 库，聚焦关键时刻 |\n| **空间构图** | 意外布局、不对称、重叠、对角线流动、打破网格 |\n| **背景细节** | 渐变网格、噪点纹理、几何图案、分层透明、戏剧性阴影 |\n\n---\n\n### 🛠️ 使用方式\n\n当你需要构建前端界面时，直接描述你的需求：\n\n```\n\"帮我做一个复古未来风格的登录页面\"\n\"需要一个极简主义的数据仪表盘\"\n\"做一个有机自然风格的个人博客首页\"\n```\n\n技能会引导生成**独特、可投入生产**的代码，而不是千篇一律的模板。\n\n---\n\n### 📋 总结\n\n| 特性 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| **目标** | 独特、高品质、生产级前端界面 |\n| **区别** | 避免通用\"AI 美学\"，强调创意和个性 |\n| **覆盖** | 组件、页面、完整应用 |\n| **技术** | HTML/CSS/JS、React、Vue 等 |\n| **重点** | 字体、颜色、动效、空间构图、背景细节 |\n\n需要我用这个技能帮你创建某个具体的界面吗？比如一个独特风格的落地页或组件？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773722251054}}
