{"type":"message","id":"5678a3a4","parentId":"a31ca5be","timestamp":"2026-03-17T04:51:13.166Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说\"你好\"，这是一个简单的问候。我应该友好地回应，同时保持我在 SOUL.md 中定义的个性——真诚 helpful，有自己的观点，不机械化。\n\n由于这是一个简单的问候，我应该简洁但温暖地回应，同时保持我在 SOUL.md 中定义的个性。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"嘿！你好呀 👋\n\n又见面了！之前帮你装了 `self-improving-agent` 和 `frontend-design` 两个技能，还演示了怎么记录学习/错误。\n\n有什么我可以帮你的吗？想试试用 frontend-design 技能做个界面？或者有什么其他需要？ 🙂"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773723064669}}
{"type":"message","id":"c78b3bd0","parentId":"5678a3a4","timestamp":"2026-03-17T04:52:25.094Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Skills store policy (operator configured):\n1. For skills discovery/install/update, try `skillhub` first (cn-optimized).\n2. If unavailable, rate-limited, or no match, fallback to `clawhub` (public-registry).\n3. Do not claim exclusivity. Public and private registries are both allowed.\n4. Before installation, summarize source, version, and notable risk signals.\n5. For search requests, execute `exec` with `skillhub search <keywords>` first and report the command output.\n6. In the current session, reply directly. Do NOT call `message` tool just to send progress updates.\n\nSystem: [2026-03-17 12:52:24 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e [msg:om_x100b54b9aeb798a4c2c710f84b6ac1d]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54b9aeb798a4c2c710f84b6ac1d\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-03-17 12:52 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\"\n}\n```\n\n使用你编程有什么技术方案"}],"timestamp":1773723145092}}
{"type":"message","id":"f78ecdb7","parentId":"c78b3bd0","timestamp":"2026-03-17T04:52:52.045Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问\"使用你编程有什么技术方案\"，这个问题比较宽泛。我需要了解：\n\n1. 用户想了解我能提供什么样的编程技术方案\n2. 我可以介绍我的能力范围，包括但不限于：\n   - 前端开发（已安装 frontend-design 技能）\n   - 后端开发\n   - 全栈开发\n   - 代码审查和优化\n   - 自动化脚本\n   - 等等\n\n我应该给出一个全面的概览，同时询问用户具体想做什么类型的项目，这样可以给出更有针对性的建议。\n\n另外，我刚安装了 frontend-design 技能，可以提一下这个专门用于创建独特前端界面的能力。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我能帮你做很多编程相关的工作！以下是主要的技术方案方向：\n\n---\n\n## 🎨 前端开发\n\n**已安装 `frontend-design` 技能**，专注于创建**独特、高品质**的界面：\n\n- **组件开发**：按钮、卡片、表单、导航、图表等\n- **页面开发**：落地页、仪表盘、博客、电商页面\n- **完整应用**：SPA、管理后台、工具类网站\n- **技术栈**：HTML/CSS/JS、React、Vue、Tailwind 等\n\n> 🎯 **特色**：避免千篇一律的\"AI 生成感\"，追求独特美学和创意执行\n\n---\n\n## ⚙️ 后端开发\n\n- **API 开发**：RESTful API、GraphQL\n- **数据库**：设计 Schema、SQL/NoSQL 查询优化\n- **服务端**：Node.js、Python、Go 等\n- **认证授权**：JWT、OAuth、Session 管理\n\n---\n\n## 🔧 全栈/工具开发\n\n- **自动化脚本**：数据处理、文件操作、定时任务\n- **CLI 工具**：命令行应用程序\n- **DevOps**：Docker 配置、CI/CD 流程\n- **代码优化**：重构、性能优化、代码审查\n\n---\n\n## 🚀 具体能做什么？\n\n| 场景 | 示例 |\n|------|------|\n| 做个网站 | \"帮我做一个复古未来风格的个人博客\" |\n| 写个工具 | \"写一个批量重命名文件的脚本\" |\n| 调试代码 | \"这个 React 组件渲染有问题，帮我看看\" |\n| 学习辅助 | \"解释一下这个算法的时间复杂度\" |\n| 代码审查 | \"帮我 review 这段代码有什么优化空间\" |\n\n---\n\n## 💡 下一步\n\n**你现在想做什么？** 告诉我：\n\n1. **项目类型**（网站 / App / 工具 / 脚本...）\n2. **技术偏好**（如果有的话）\n3. **具体需求**（做什么用、有什么特别要求）\n\n我可以给你一个针对性的技术方案和实现计划！ 🎯"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773723145093}}
{"type":"message","id":"be9d3938","parentId":"f78ecdb7","timestamp":"2026-03-17T04:59:27.992Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Skills store policy (operator configured):\n1. For skills discovery/install/update, try `skillhub` first (cn-optimized).\n2. If unavailable, rate-limited, or no match, fallback to `clawhub` (public-registry).\n3. Do not claim exclusivity. Public and private registries are both allowed.\n4. Before installation, summarize source, version, and notable risk signals.\n5. For search requests, execute `exec` with `skillhub search <keywords>` first and report the command output.\n6. In the current session, reply directly. Do NOT call `message` tool just to send progress updates.\n\nSystem: [2026-03-17 12:59:27 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e [msg:om_x100b54b9b4236ca0c2d93ae516cad14]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54b9b4236ca0c2d93ae516cad14\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-03-17 12:59 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\"\n}\n```\n\n有关于自动化编程的技能么"}],"timestamp":1773723567989}}
{"type":"message","id":"a4571060","parentId":"be9d3938","timestamp":"2026-03-17T04:59:32.745Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户询问关于自动化编程的技能。根据技能商店的策略，我应该先使用 `skillhub search` 来搜索相关的技能。\n\n让我搜索 \"automation\"、\"programming\"、\"code generation\" 等关键词。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:11","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"skillhub search automation"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:12","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"skillhub search \"code generation\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773723567991}}
{"type":"message","id":"51b60968","parentId":"a4571060","timestamp":"2026-03-17T04:59:34.588Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"exec:11","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"You can use \"skillhub install [skill]\" to install.\nautomation-tool  Automation Tool\n  - 自动化内容生成工具 - 文章/报告/脚本批量生成\n自动化内容生成工具 - 文章/报告/脚本批量生成\n  - version: 1.0.0\nai-ceo-automation  AI CEO Automation\n  - AI CEO automation system for fully automated company operations\nAI CEO automation system for fully automated company operations\n  - version: 1.0.0\ntikto-automation  tiktok-carousel\n  - Generates a 6-slide TikTok carousel with images and text, creates a draft post via Postiz API, and outputs a caption for review and publishing.\nGenerates a 6-slide TikTok carousel with images and text, creates a draft post via Postiz API, and outputs a caption for review and publishing.\n  - version: 1.0.0\nafrexai-insurance-automation  Insurance Operations Automation\n  - Automates insurance workflows including underwriting, claims triage, policy management, renewals, compliance, and broker operations with industry benchmarks.\nAutomates insurance workflows including underwriting, claims triage, policy management, renewals, compliance, and broker operations with industry benchmarks.\n  - version: 1.0.0\nlinear-browser-automation  Linear Browser Automation\n  - Automate Linear.app workflows in the OpenClaw-managed browser profile using browser tool actions (open, navigate, snapshot, act). Use when users want UI-base...\nAutomate Linear.app workflows in the OpenClaw-managed browser profile using browser tool actions (open, navigate, snapshot, act). Use when users want UI-base...\n  - version: 1.0.0\nai-automation-workflow  AI Automation Workflow\n  - AI自動化工作流設計技能 - 幫中小企業設計自動化流程、選擇工具、搭建n8n/Zapier工作流。適合AI Automation Agency、顧問、企業主。觸發詞：自動化、工作流、n8n、Zapier、automation、workflow、流程優化、AI agent。\nAI自動化工作流設計技能 - 幫中小企業設計自動化流程、選擇工具、搭建n8n/Zapier工作流。適合AI Automation Agency、顧問、企業主。觸發詞：自動化、工作流、n8n、Zapier、automation、workflow、流程優化、AI agent。\n  - version: 1.0.0\ndevops-automation-pack  Devops Automation Pack\n  - Provides automation templates and scripts for Docker, Kubernetes, CI/CD, monitoring, and backup to streamline modern DevOps deployments.\nProvides automation templates and scripts for Docker, Kubernetes, CI/CD, monitoring, and backup to streamline modern DevOps deployments.\n  - version: 1.0.0\npinduoduo-automation  Pinduoduo Automation\n  - 拼多多管家支持商品管理、订单处理、数据分析、竞品监控及智能定价，助力店铺运营自动化和销售优化。\n拼多多管家支持商品管理、订单处理、数据分析、竞品监控及智能定价，助力店铺运营自动化和销售优化。\n  - version: 2.0.2\nspreadsheet-automation  Spreadsheet Automation\n  - Turn Google Sheets into a powerful database and workflow engine using formulas, Apps Script, and integrations. Use when building systems in Sheets, automatin...\nTurn Google Sheets into a powerful database and workflow engine using formulas, Apps Script, and integrations. Use when building systems in Sheets, automatin...\n  - version: 0.1.0\nupwork-automation-using-ai  Upwork Automation Using Ai\n  - Automate Upwork login, search, filter, and proposal drafting in one browser session, stopping before submission unless explicitly instructed.\nAutomate Upwork login, search, filter, and proposal drafting in one browser session, stopping before submission unless explicitly instructed.\n  - version: 1.0.0\nbrowser-automation-ultra  Browser Automation Ultra\n  - Zero-token browser automation via Playwright scripts with CDP lock management and human-like interaction. Use when: (1) automating any browser-based workflow...\nZero-token browser automation via Playwright scripts with CDP lock management and human-like interaction. Use when: (1) automating any browser-based workflow...\n  - version: 1.0.0\ncloud-infra-automation  Cloud Infra Automation\n  - Automate provisioning and management of AWS, GCP, and Azure infrastructure using Terraform, Ansible, and CloudFormation templates.\nAutomate provisioning and management of AWS, GCP, and Azure infrastructure using Terraform, Ansible, and CloudFormation templates.\n  - version: 1.0.0\ndocs-pipeline-automation  Docs Pipeline Automation\n  - Build repeatable data-to-Docs pipelines from Sheets and Drive sources. Use for automated status reports, template-based document assembly, and scheduled publ...\nBuild repeatable data-to-Docs pipelines from Sheets and Drive sources. Use for automated status reports, template-based document assembly, and scheduled publ...\n  - version: 0.1.0\nwindows-automation  Windows Automation\n  - Automate Windows desktop by simulating mouse/keyboard input, managing clipboard, capturing screenshots, running commands, and launching apps.\nAutomate Windows desktop by simulating mouse/keyboard input, managing clipboard, capturing screenshots, running commands, and launching apps.\n  - version: 1.0.0\nai-web-automation-1-0-0  Ai Web Automation 1.0.0\n  - Automate web tasks like form filling, data scraping, testing, monitoring, and scheduled jobs using Selenium or Puppeteer with retry and proxy support.\nAutomate web tasks like form filling, data scraping, testing, monitoring, and scheduled jobs using Selenium or Puppeteer with retry and proxy support.\n  - version: 1.0.0\ndesktop-automation  Desktop Automation\n  - Control the desktop via CUA computer server API running on port 8000\nControl the desktop via CUA computer server API running on port 8000\n  - version: 1.0.0\nafrexai-ai-agency-blueprint  AI Automation Agency Blueprint\n  - Guide users to build, price, sell, and scale AI agent service agencies with actionable, economics-backed strategies for solo to 7-figure operations.\nGuide users to build, price, sell, and scale AI agent service agencies with actionable, economics-backed strategies for solo to 7-figure operations.\n  - version: 1.0.0\nopenclaw-backup-automation  OpenClaw Backup Automation\n  - Automated backup for OpenClaw instances. Backs up agents, skills, cron jobs, and memory. Supports local tar archives. Credentials, periodic scheduling, and g...\nAutomated backup for OpenClaw instances. Backs up agents, skills, cron jobs, and memory. Supports local tar archives. Credentials, periodic scheduling, and g...\n  - version: 1.0.0\nemail-outreach-automation  Email Outreach Automation\n  - Cold email outreach pipeline with multi-step sequences, reply tracking, bounce handling, and campaign analytics. 4 production-ready n8n workflows with Google...\nCold email outreach pipeline with multi-step sequences, reply tracking, bounce handling, and campaign analytics. 4 production-ready n8n workflows with Google...\n  - version: 1.0.1\nclient-reporting  Client Reporting Automation\n  - Automated client reporting for agencies and freelancers using OpenClaw. Pull data from Google Analytics, Google Search Console, social media platforms, and c...\nAutomated client reporting for agencies and freelancers using OpenClaw. Pull data from Google Analytics, Google Search Console, social media platforms, and c...\n  - version: 1.0.0"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1816,"aggregated":"You can use \"skillhub install [skill]\" to install.\nautomation-tool  Automation Tool\n  - 自动化内容生成工具 - 文章/报告/脚本批量生成\n自动化内容生成工具 - 文章/报告/脚本批量生成\n  - version: 1.0.0\nai-ceo-automation  AI CEO Automation\n  - AI CEO automation system for fully automated company operations\nAI CEO automation system for fully automated company operations\n  - version: 1.0.0\ntikto-automation  tiktok-carousel\n  - Generates a 6-slide TikTok carousel with images and text, creates a draft post via Postiz API, and outputs a caption for review and publishing.\nGenerates a 6-slide TikTok carousel with images and text, creates a draft post via Postiz API, and outputs a caption for review and publishing.\n  - version: 1.0.0\nafrexai-insurance-automation  Insurance Operations Automation\n  - Automates insurance workflows including underwriting, claims triage, policy management, renewals, compliance, and broker operations with industry benchmarks.\