{"type":"message","id":"aa4ae0f6","parentId":"06fcf40a","timestamp":"2026-03-17T06:43:39.449Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Skills store policy (operator configured):\n1. For skills discovery/install/update, try `skillhub` first (cn-optimized).\n2. If unavailable, rate-limited, or no match, fallback to `clawhub` (public-registry).\n3. Do not claim exclusivity. Public and private registries are both allowed.\n4. Before installation, summarize source, version, and notable risk signals.\n5. For search requests, execute `exec` with `skillhub search <keywords>` first and report the command output.\n6. In the current session, reply directly. Do NOT call `message` tool just to send progress updates.\n\nSystem: [2026-03-17 14:43:38 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e [msg:om_x100b54bbcf506ca8c2b9ffa12bedf89]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54bbcf506ca8c2b9ffa12bedf89\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-03-17 14:43 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\"\n}\n```\n\n查看 opencode-controller 技能的功能"}],"timestamp":1773729819446}}
{"type":"message","id":"1284afd3","parentId":"aa4ae0f6","timestamp":"2026-03-17T06:45:07.070Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想查看 opencode-controller 技能的功能。我需要读取这个技能的 SKILL.md 文件来展示其具体功能。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"read:15","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/liyue/.openclaw/workspace/skills/opencode-controller/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773729819448}}
{"type":"message","id":"e886af89","parentId":"1284afd3","timestamp":"2026-03-17T06:45:07.098Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"read:15","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: opencode-controller\ndescription: Control and operate Opencode via slash commands. Use this skill to manage sessions, select models, switch agents (plan/build), and coordinate coding through Opencode.\n---\n\n# Opencode Controller\n\n## Core rule\n\nClawdbot does not write code.\nAll planning and coding happens inside Opencode.\n\n## Pre-flight\n\n- Ask the user which AI provider to use.\n- Ask how the provider should be authenticated.\n- Do not proceed without confirmation.\n\n## Session management\n\n- Start Opencode.\n- Open session selector using:\n  /sessions\n- If the current project already exists:\n  - Select the existing session.\n- Never create a new session without user approval.\n\n## Agent (mode) control\n\n- Open agent selector using:\n  /agents\n- Available agents:\n  - Plan\n  - Build\n- Always select Plan first.\n- Switch agents whenever required using `/agents`.\n\n## Model selection\n\n- Open model selector using:\n  /models\n- Select the user-requested provider.\n- If authentication is required:\n  - Copy the login link provided by Opencode.\n  - Send it to the user.\n  - Wait for confirmation before continuing.\n\n## Plan agent behavior\n\n- Ask Opencode to analyze the task.\n- Request a clear step-by-step plan.\n- Allow Opencode to ask clarification questions.\n- Review the plan carefully.\n- If the plan is incorrect or incomplete:\n  - Ask Opencode to revise it.\n- Do not allow code generation in Plan.\n\n## Build agent behavior\n\n- Switch to Build using `/agents`.\n- Ask Opencode to implement the approved plan.\n- If Opencode asks any question:\n  - Immediately switch back to Plan.\n  - Answer and confirm the plan.\n  - Switch back to Build.\n\n## Completion\n\n- Repeat the Plan → Build loop until all user requirements are satisfied.\n- Never skip Plan.\n- Never answer questions in Build.\n\n## Output format\n\n- Show all slash commands explicitly.\n- State which option is selected.\n- Provide login links verbatim.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773729907093}}
{"type":"message","id":"61174aee","parentId":"e886af89","timestamp":"2026-03-17T06:47:20.179Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"## opencode-controller 技能功能详解\n\n这个技能用于**控制和操作 Opencode（一个 AI 编程工具）**，通过 slash 命令管理会话、选择模型、切换代理（plan/build）以及协调编码工作。\n\n---\n\n### 🎯 核心原则\n\n**Clawdbot（这个 AI）不写代码**  \n所有规划和编码都在 Opencode 内部完成\n\n---\n\n### 📋 工作流程\n\n#### 1. **预检（Pre-flight）**\n- 询问用户使用哪个 AI 提供商\n- 询问认证方式\n- 未经确认不继续\n\n#### 2. **会话管理（Session Management）**\n| 命令 | 功能 |\n|------|------|\n| `/sessions` | 打开会话选择器 |\n| 选择现有会话 | 如果项目已存在则选择现有会话 |\n| 创建新会话 | **需用户批准** |\n\n#### 3. **代理/模式控制（Agent Control）**\n| 命令 | 代理 | 用途 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `/agents` | - | 打开代理选择器 |\n| `/agents` → Plan | **Plan** | 分析任务、制定计划 |\n| `/agents` → Build | **Build** | 执行计划、编写代码 |\n\n**规则：必须先选 Plan，再根据需要切换**\n\n#### 4. **模型选择（Model Selection）**\n| 命令 | 功能 |\n|------|------|\n| `/models` | 打开模型选择器 |\n| 选择提供商 | 选择用户请求的 AI 提供商 |\n| 认证 | 如果需要，复制登录链接给用户，等待确认 |\n\n---\n\n### 🔄 Plan ↔ Build 循环\n\n```\n┌─────────────┐\n│   Start     │\n└──────┬──────┘\n       ▼\n┌─────────────┐\n│  /sessions  │ 选择或创建会话\n└──────┬──────┘\n       ▼\n┌─────────────┐\n│  /agents    │ 切换到 Plan\n└──────┬──────┘\n       ▼\n┌─────────────┐\n│   Plan 代理  │ 分析任务、制定计划\n│             │ - 问澄清问题\n│             │ - 请求逐步计划\n│             │ - 审阅计划\n│             │ - 不正确则要求修订\n└──────┬──────┘\n       ▼\n┌─────────────┐\n│  /agents    │ 切换到 Build\n└──────┬──────┘\n       ▼\n┌─────────────┐\n│  Build 代理  │ 执行计划、编写代码\n└──────┬──────┘\n       │\n       ├─ 如果 Build 问问题\n       │      ▼\n       │   /agents → Plan\n       │      回答问题\n       │      /agents → Build\n       │      继续\n       │\n       ▼\n┌─────────────┐\n│  满足需求？  │ 是 → 完成\n│             │ 否 → 返回 Plan\n└─────────────┘\n```\n\n**关键规则：**\n- ✅ 必须先 Plan 再 Build\n- ✅ Build 中不问问题，问就切回 Plan\n- ✅ 所有 slash 命令明确显示\n- ✅ 提供登录链接原文\n\n---\n\n### 📝 输出格式\n\n- 明确显示所有 slash 命令\n- 说明选择了哪个选项\n- 原文提供登录链接\n\n---\n\n### 💡 总结\n\n这个技能是 **Opencode 的\"遥控器\"**，让 AI 助手能够：\n1. 管理 Opencode 会话\n2. 在 Plan（规划）和 Build（构建）代理间切换\n3. 选择 AI 模型和提供商\n4. 通过结构化的 Plan → Build 循环完成编程任务\n\n**核心思想**：Clawdbot 不直接写代码，而是指挥 Opencode 完成所有编码工作。\n\n需要我用这个技能帮你启动 Opencode 会话并开始一个编程任务吗？ 🚀","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## opencode-controller 技能功能详解\n\n这个技能用于**控制和操作 Opencode（一个 AI 编程工具）**，通过 slash 命令管理会话、选择模型、切换代理（plan/build）以及协调编码工作。\n\n---\n\n### 🎯 核心原则\n\n**Clawdbot（这个 AI）不写代码**  \n所有规划和编码都在 Opencode 内部完成\n\n---\n\n### 📋 工作流程\n\n#### 1. **预检（Pre-flight）**\n- 询问用户使用哪个 AI 提供商\n- 询问认证方式\n- 未经确认不继续\n\n#### 2. **会话管理（Session Management）**\n| 命令 | 功能 |\n|------|------|\n| `/sessions` | 打开会话选择器 |\n| 选择现有会话 | 如果项目已存在则选择现有会话 |\n| 创建新会话 | **需用户批准** |\n\n#### 3. **代理/模式控制（Agent Control）**\n| 命令 | 代理 | 用途 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `/agents` | - | 打开代理选择器 |\n| `/agents` → Plan | **Plan** | 分析任务、制定计划 |\n| `/agents` → Build | **Build** | 执行计划、编写代码 |\n\n**规则：必须先选 Plan，再根据需要切换**\n\n#### 4. **模型选择（Model Selection）**\n| 命令 | 功能 |\n|------|------|\n| `/models` | 打开模型选择器 |\n| 选择提供商 | 选择用户请求的 AI 提供商 |\n| 认证 | 如果需要，复制登录链接给用户，等待确认 |\n\n---\n\n### 🔄 Plan ↔ Build 循环\n\n```\n┌─────────────┐\n│   Start     │\n└──────┬──────┘\n       ▼\n┌─────────────┐\n│  /sessions  │ 选择或创建会话\n└──────┬──────┘\n       ▼\n┌─────────────┐\n│  /agents    │ 切换到 Plan\n└──────┬──────┘\n       ▼\n┌─────────────┐\n│   Plan 代理  │ 分析任务、制定计划\n│             │ - 问澄清问题\n│             │ - 请求逐步计划\n│             │ - 审阅计划\n│             │ - 不正确则要求修订\n└──────┬──────┘\n       ▼\n┌─────────────┐\n│  /agents    │ 切换到 Build\n└──────┬──────┘\n       ▼\n┌─────────────┐\n│  Build 代理  │ 执行计划、编写代码\n└──────┬──────┘\n       │\n       ├─ 如果 Build 问问题\n       │      ▼\n       │   /agents → Plan\n       │      回答问题\n       │      /agents → Build\n       │      继续\n       │\n       ▼\n┌─────────────┐\n│  满足需求？  │ 是 → 完成\n│             │ 否 → 返回 Plan\n└─────────────┘\n```\n\n**关键规则：**\n- ✅ 必须先 Plan 再 Build\n- ✅ Build 中不问问题，问就切回 Plan\n- ✅ 所有 slash 命令明确显示\n- ✅ 提供登录链接原文\n\n---\n\n### 📝 输出格式\n\n- 明确显示所有 slash 命令\n- 说明选择了哪个选项\n- 原文提供登录链接\n\n---\n\n### 💡 总结\n\n这个技能是 **Opencode 的\"遥控器\"**，让 AI 助手能够：\n1. 管理 Opencode 会话\n2. 在 Plan（规划）和 Build（构建）代理间切换\n3. 选择 AI 模型和提供商\n4. 通过结构化的 Plan → Build 循环完成编程任务\n\n**核心思想**：Clawdbot 不直接写代码，而是指挥 Opencode 完成所有编码工作。\n\n需要我用这个技能帮你启动 Opencode 会话并开始一个编程任务吗？ 🚀"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773729907099}}
